{"tid":910696,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"【外星人】世界上有無外星人? 如果有, 點解外星人無和我們接觸?","createTime":"2018-11-21T11:07:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-30T18:57:59.000Z","uid":78029,"like":42,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"f1e3c64be1571e795a7d98bdc2cd9b5cb846e04d","tid":910696,"uid":78029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T11:07:41.000Z","msg":"大家好，又係小弟，小弟開咗個Youtube channel ，希望分享吓有趣小知識(心理學, 科學, 歷史, 甚至政治)<br />\n<br />\n今次講吓科學界點睇「世界上有無外星人? 如果有, 點解外星人無和我們接觸?」呢個問題<br />\n<br />\n今次轉咗用動畫形式，第一次用，唔係好識用，所以想知大家意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如有不足, 麻煩指正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3ob8lj7OM5Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D3ob8lj7OM5Q&d=WFg%2BS0Xu3VzYSHNt7AiMIwtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=df03d884\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3ob8lj7OM5Q</a><br />\n<br />\n上次想講吓近年科學點睇「成年後腦袋係咪不再進步, 只會退化?」呢個問題, 從而介紹吓 我地可以點樣增加記憶力<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=21byiVTSZhI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D21byiVTSZhI&d=WFg%2BS0Xu3VzYSHNt7AiMIwtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=3b72f0e1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=21byiVTSZhI</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上上次由大腦科學角度講吓靈魂出竅/離體經驗係咩一回事, 科學界有無方法重現靈魂出竅<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JhjpNvT-U4g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DJhjpNvT-U4g&d=WFg%2BS0Xu3VzYSHNt7AiMIwtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=eec12b3a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JhjpNvT-U4g</a><br />\n<br />\n上上上次由大腦科學角度講吓一D因為腦部受傷而成為奇才的人, 從而睇下未來科技有無可能將我地由普通人突然變成奇才<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eCEv3hfdco8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DeCEv3hfdco8&d=WFg%2BS0Xu3VzYSHNt7AiMIwtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=d7a343ad\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eCEv3hfdco8</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最早一次係由由大腦科學, 心理學角度講吓愛情行為, 例如點解分手咁痛苦, 點解開始拍拖時會睇唔到對方缺點: <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mgTq1gYCsZA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DmgTq1gYCsZA&d=WFg%2BS0Xu3VzYSHNt7AiMIwtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=86b4723b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mgTq1gYCsZA</a>"},{"pid":"5dd32ca2dd6e9a24fb9884daf893ceb1d38a1d2e","tid":910696,"uid":78029,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T11:09:51.000Z","msg":"另外,  SETI（搜尋地外文明）計劃, 呢個計劃係比大家可以用自己部腦幫手搵有無外星人消息<br />\n<a href=\"http://setiathome.berkeley.edu/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsetiathome.berkeley.edu%2F&d=WFg%2BS0Xu3VzYSHNt7AiMIwtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=235d269b\" target=\"_blank\">http://setiathome.berkeley.edu/</a>"},{"pid":"1525cf2306fa49058be139c4d0f23f8ffa2d81ae","tid":910696,"uid":135443,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T11:13:17.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbe3998a1368d05deda0784669fd36ba7aee13a4","tid":910696,"uid":78029,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"1525cf2306fa49058be139c4d0f23f8ffa2d81ae","tid":910696,"uid":135443,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T11:13:17.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T11:23:41.000Z","msg":"多謝絲打支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"558baf2363cd05ccae8bcafaa15396f7a673b854","tid":910696,"uid":78029,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T11:55:11.000Z","msg":"推一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e1df192640dc4f0e321430b15086e5e4d21491c","tid":910696,"uid":130821,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T12