Z","msg":"繼續推一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6245063b9eed01519465da653d5948c67ffe41cc","tid":910696,"uid":195267,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T13:54:05.000Z","msg":"之前睇過一個理論幾有趣，話宇宙實在太大<br />\n話地球離其他星球/星系太遠，從外星睇到的地球其實係幾千幾萬年前未有人類的情況，因為光線係經過好耐至傳送到去咁遠的星球"},{"pid":"cb0cc8b64615d3a84b7db713fb1cb885887c1c51","tid":910696,"uid":78029,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6245063b9eed01519465da653d5948c67ffe41cc","tid":910696,"uid":195267,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T13:54:05.000Z","msg":"之前睇過一個理論幾有趣，話宇宙實在太大<br />\n話地球離其他星球/星系太遠，從外星睇到的地球其實係幾千幾萬年前未有人類的情況，因為光線係經過好耐至傳送到去咁遠的星球"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T14:02:16.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打留言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係呀, 呢個真架, 因為宇宙真係好大, 例如銀河系直徑估計係100,000光年至180,000光年, 即係光由「圓」心飛到去外邊都要50,000至90,000年<br />\n而銀河系都只一千億之中一個星系<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以宇宙真係好大,  大家觀星睇到D光都好有歷史架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n隨時而家睇到D星星收咗皮好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n至於外星人(假設有)觀察地球, 其實佢地有無能力飛嚟都未知, 因為宇宙距離太大, 都唔知有無文明可以發展星際旅遊技術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b6115ae08d7dad5f510d5d3e88cb5c33c2cfe4c","tid":910696,"uid":204533,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T14:14:37.000Z","msg":"動畫唔錯, 但係某啲位飛得太快, 特別係某啲字同數字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有巴打啲讀音咬字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ae02eab1c72494d96b973e7b29206e0ec0f9932","tid":910696,"uid":78029,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8b6115ae08d7dad5f510d5d3e88cb5c33c2cfe4c","tid":910696,"uid":204533,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T14:14:37.000Z","msg":"動畫唔錯, 但係某啲位飛得太快, 特別係某啲字同數字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有巴打啲讀音咬字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T14:56:02.000Z","msg":"多謝絲打意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n動畫方面下次會改善, 因為第一次用, 唔太識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n至於咬字要比多少少時間我去改<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7db23463bc77ce88c6a987bc6aefac9a475bc2b4","tid":910696,"uid":78029,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T15:21:29.000Z","msg":"推一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fba187905f0a477c07179ba5551a82aa4741c363","tid":910696,"uid":78029,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T15:53:48.000Z","msg":"又推一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"612bec3fda6691948dab2b3ce5128c0fe4dd6225","tid":910696,"uid":25118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T15:56:44.000Z","msg":"無接觸可能係一件好事，請參考「黑暗叢林法則」"},{"pid":"6a22e0402bf7f3c57605a606f5211a7f531fded8","tid":910696,"uid":78029,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"612bec3fda6691948dab2b3ce5128c0fe4dd6225","tid":910696,"uid":25118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T15:56:44.000Z","msg":"無接觸可能係一件好事，請參考「黑暗叢林法則」"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T16:09:46.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打留言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n的確係, 因為可以嚟到地球的話, 佢地好有可能先進過我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n加上語言不通, 任何一個舉動都可能被詮譯做攻擊, 可能引起戰爭<br />\n<br />\n除此之外, 有科學家提過即使見唔到活生生外星文明, 但搵到佢地遺跡都唔係好事<br />\n因為咁可能證實咗大過濾理論, 證實人類都難以過避免滅絕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7980f2b3ba0c0543bd78a6a910cff78cf333528","tid":910696,"uid":84159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T16:21:21.000Z","msg":"其實係佢地太低科技 出唔到佢地自己既行星"},{"pid":"f9bed7cd98c83a2bf6476b6a3cb4d6a34e056fc7","tid":910696,"uid":78029,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"c7980f2b3ba0c0543bd78a6a910cff78cf333528","tid":910696,"uid":84159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T16:21:21.000Z","msg":"其實係佢地太低科技 出唔到佢地自己既行星"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T16:41:45.000Z","msg":"多謝絲打留言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有可能係咁, 但亦有可能係飛出咗自己行星, 但飛唔出自己星系<br />\n原因係可能有啲物理上的限制<br />\n<br />\n上面提到即使係光咁快, 飛出一個星系閒閒地都要上萬年計, 咁點做跨星系旅遊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當然有D朋友會諗好似復仇者1 咁整個蟲洞,  但理論上蟲洞會將通過既物件壓扁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以可能真係物理上有極限令星際旅遊好難實現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d6764a0f8f9adb7a7ce083b15282d9a83570e99","tid":910696,"uid":78029,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T17:21:58.000Z","msg":"瞓前推一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd97edcbffb4f93c8fc543d8e6e86c5a16ca93a9","tid":910696,"uid":71712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T17:31:05.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"3fa79e48544a30d5a2464993712822e1a0c84393","tid":910696,"uid":64894,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T17:32:45.000Z","msg":"十卜，最憎啲超自然醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc87a0177ccbcfbc5c6f2ae3bec73f259d49f07c","tid":910696,"uid":64894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T17:33:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>十卜，最憎啲超自然撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"657a1293c01fa7a5cea34c8ee0a19f040100e363","tid":910696,"uid":78029,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"3fa79e48544a30d5a2464993712822e1a0c84393","tid":910696,"uid":64894,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T17:32:45.000Z","msg":"十卜，最憎啲超自然醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T04:28:12.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過傾外星人呢個話題, 唔一定超自然, 係可以比較科學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b46272c775cab186b72b14d52412f6729bc9e6b4","tid":910696,"uid":195267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T06:21:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.spacetelescope.org/images/heic1502a/zoomable/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.spacetelescope.org%2Fimages%2Fheic1502a%2Fzoomable%2F&d=WFg%2BS0Xu3VzYSHNt7AiMIwtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=868b74e3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.spacetelescope.org/images/heic1502a/zoomable/</a><br />\n哈勃太空望遠鏡影左仙女座星系的一部分, 呢張超巨形相片有成15億pixels<br />\n圖中大約40000光年的距離, 包含超過15億粒恆星<br />\nzoom埋去睇恆星好似多到好似沙一樣, 當中有多少行星<br />\n其中一粒行星有外星生物絕對不出奇"},{"pid":"93185ea49fa28cea1d5d06555584aa5a5e51c145","tid":910696,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T09:14:27.000Z","msg":"more"},{"pid":"bdbcc2c94340cc02c1302a5c13bba5e44016b86b","tid":910696,"uid":78029,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"b46272c775cab186b72b14d52412f6729bc9e6b4","tid":910696,"uid":195267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T06:21:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.spacetelescope.org/images/heic1502a/zoomable/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.spacetelescope.org%2Fimages%2Fheic1502a%2Fzoomable%2F&d=WFg%2BS0Xu3VzYSHNt7AiMIwtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=868b74e3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.spacetelescope.org/images/heic1502a/zoomable/</a><br />\n哈勃太空望遠鏡影左仙女座星系的一部分, 呢張超巨形相片有成15億pixels<br />\n圖中大約40000光年的距離, 包含超過15億粒恆星<br />\nzoom埋去睇恆星好似多到好似沙一樣, 當中有多少行星<br />\n其中一粒行星有外星生物絕對不出奇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T10:30:43.000Z","msg":"啱呀<br />\n睇過書<br />\n有科學家估計地球沙粒數量係10^18粒, 但行星數量係10^21粒<br />\n所以, 恆河沙數都唔夠形容<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過, 如果真係好好好好好好悲觀<br />\n認為10^-22次(0.0000000000000000000001)的機會先孕育出高智慧文明 <br />\n咁可能真係無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但係, 10^-22次基本上細到接近0, 而且亦解釋唔到點解地球會孕育出高智慧文明 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e01efba2109777bfcf6a5c9369759b0397797df","tid":910696,"uid":8377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T10:55:36.000Z","msg":"有d professor pow pow 既feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c38784552ff1045a7959daadb0d2df14fc869b3","tid":910696,"uid":78029,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"93185ea49fa28cea1d5d06555584aa5a5e51c145","tid":910696,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T09:14:27.000Z","msg":"more"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T11:51:38.000Z","msg":"多謝絲打留言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ada5d15d14698f4d08b1270a5cb701ac28a8431","tid":910696,"uid":78029,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"5e01efba2109777bfcf6a5c9369759b0397797df","tid":910696,"uid":8377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T10:55:36.000Z","msg":"有d professor pow pow 既feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T11:52:17.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打留言<br />\n竟然係似pow pow <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1bc956b4eca9aba94747bd23761af61a3e2f50c","tid":910696,"uid":78029,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T13:56:51.000Z","msg":"推一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa5922204620f6b86a056264f51e760d464f9578","tid":910696,"uid":46500,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T14:16:37.000Z","msg":"黑暗森林理論似乎係最好嘅解釋<