":"咬字加油"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T15:37:06.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n努力中, 我而家發覺要好刻意咁減慢語速先可以較為清楚, 但都只係較為<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ca86111cac78dd04bff66a7bc0c43561c4fe4cf","tid":910696,"uid":175004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T15:42:45.000Z","msg":"哈哈 有MIB係到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d98d567aba3349e30d71776f3bd408999f2944d","tid":910696,"uid":145362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T16:06:35.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n有諗過外星文明已經發展到好勁，覺得人類就好似螞蟻咁，連觀察都覺得浪費時間"},{"pid":"0a3819f6ef2cce97d9773aa142eb04acac616b66","tid":910696,"uid":110832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T16:18:56.000Z","msg":"人類被創造果時已經鎖住左大腦功能<br />\n所以大腦功能基本上係不能再開發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n就好似啲垃圾政府咁<br />\n想要啲人民剛好懂得操作機械就夠"},{"pid":"f63f40040c27f6d9add306b5f3b582f5a3722d7b","tid":910696,"uid":140234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T16:26:06.000Z","msg":"因為人類唔團結"},{"pid":"ed7896bab1e74b012be0fef6c5117ad37333072d","tid":910696,"uid":1188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T16:31:04.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"d05e16b4df4e4e0f61216b80f4de8cc0488ba005","tid":910696,"uid":1482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T16:36:53.000Z","msg":"有可能宇宙只不過係外星人既一個實驗"},{"pid":"09e236301eacf54633ef9e5c1e535de90692a7ee","tid":910696,"uid":36866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T16:41:42.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"07f2c918b44ecb9f9bc5be6d40f7c9eaa2a41177","tid":910696,"uid":220853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T17:07:15.000Z","msg":"因為 自由意志 必須被尊重<br />\n而佢地不被允許侵犯人類既自由意志"},{"pid":"0c0ca09afedec397c90919fcd98f9a35cfae98e8","tid":910696,"uid":109864,"lik